NK041(di)021:1: // dpal mgon 'phags pa klu sgrub zhal snga nas brgyud
NK041(di)021:2: pa'i sgrol ma g.yul bzlog bltas chog tu bkod pa
NK041(di)021:3: bden 'bras myur ston ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK041(di)021:4: na mo gu ru +aar+ya t+aa ra ye /
NK041(di)021:5: dpa' zhing glog ltar myur ba'i thugs rje'i spyan //
NK041(di)021:6: mkha' khyab sdug bsngal yid can la gzigs pas //
NK041(di)021:7: skad cig re rer rnam grol bde ba cher //
NK041(di)021:8: dbugs 'byin stsol mdzad rje btsun 'phags mar 'dud //
NK041(di)021:9: gang de'i rnal 'byor la brten nas //
NK041(di)021:10: phyi nang bar chad bzlog pa'i thabs //
NK041(di)021:11: khungs ldan byin rlabs gzi brjid can //
NK041(di)021:13: rgyal ba gnyis pa 'phags mchog klu sgrub zhabs nas
NK041(di)021:14: rim par brgyud cing 'phags bod kyi ljongs na yongs
NK041(di)021:15: su grags pa'i mdos zlog 'di la don bzhi /
NK041(di)021:17: phan yod dang 'brel ba'i lo rgyus /
NK041(di)021:18: sgrub pa po'i gang zag chog dngos lag tu len pa'i tshul lo //
NK041(di)021:20: rgyal bas lung bstan cing sgrol ma'i rgyud la brten
NK041(di)021:21: nas grub pa thob pa 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis
NK041(di)021:22: mdzad de skal ldan rnams la gnang /
NK041(di)021:23: de nas brgyud pa'i zam ma chad par byon te jo bo rje a ti shas bod du bsnams /
NK041(di)021:24: jo bos sku gshegs khar na baza'i gseb nas bton te dge bshes ston pa la gnang /
NK041(di)021:25: des gsang phu ba rngog legs pa'i shes rab /
NK041(di)021:26: des sne zur ba la gnang zhing rim par brgyud
NK041(di)021:27: nas rgya ston la bka' babs te yig cha rgyas
NK041(di)021:28: pa'ang mdzad / phyis rgyal tshab grags pa mchog dbyangs
NK041(di)021:29: dang zhu chen sogs kyis yig cha lag len rgyas
NK041(di)021:30: bsdus ci rigs par mdzad cing lung dang lag len
NK041(di)021:31: gyi brgyud pa'ang ma nyams par bzhugs pa'o //
NK041(di)021:33: 'phags pa klu sgrub kyi zhal nas //
NK041(di)021:34: ye shes lha dang 'jig rten pa //
NK041(di)021:35: de dag nus pa 'di yis zhi //
NK041(di)021:36: klu rgyal gtsug gi nor bu bzhin //
NK041(di)021:38: rten gsum 'og tu mnan pa dang //
NK041(di)021:39: sde brgyad dag la gtad pa dang //
NK041(di)021:40: zor thun phur pa bsgril ba dang //
NK041(di)021:41: yul du ltas ngan skyes pa sogs //
NK041(di)021:42: de dag kun gyi nus pa ni //
NK041(di)021:43: cung zad tsam yang 'byin mi nus //
NK041(di)021:44: rang nyid bsgrubs na mchog tu basngagasa //
NK041(di)021:47: thag ring por 'gro na cho ga 'di byas pas rkyen ngan gang yang mi 'byung ngo //
NK041(di)021:48: yang yul phyogs su 'khrugs pa yod pa dang /
NK041(di)021:50: mi dge ba'i ltas byung ba la cho ga 'dis zlog go //
NK041(di)021:51: rang la mi 'dod pa ci byung yang the tshom
NK041(di)021:52: mi byed par cho ga 'di bgyis pas rang ci
NK041(di)021:54: 'dod pa'i don sgrub pa dang zlog pa'i cho ga
NK041(di)021:55: 'di las byin rlabs che ba mthu che ba med
NK041(di)021:56: pas / 'di la shin tu brtson par gyis shig /
NK041(di)021:57: bod du thon pa'i yig cha 'di las zab pa med par 'dug gsungs so //
NK041(di)021:58: des na mthu dang byad kha than ltas rmi lam ngan pa /
NK041(di)021:60: gdon chen gyi gnod pa zug pa /
NK041(di)021:63: lo zla zhag dus gza' skar ngan pa'i gnod pa
NK041(di)021:64: sogs gang la'ang zlog pa 'di zab cing stobs che
NK041(di)021:65: / gzhan yang drag sngags bgrang ba dang /
NK041(di)021:67: thag ring 'gro ba'i nyes pa sogs kyang sgrib cing
NK041(di)021:68: mdor na ye shes pa dang 'jig rten pa thams
NK041(di)021:69: cad zlog cing dge legs thams cad spel ba la
NK041(di)021:71: de lta bu'i byin rlabs phan yon chen po dang
NK041(di)021:72: ldan pa'i cho ga 'di nyid byas pas yid ches
NK041(di)021:73: pa'i rtags rgya gar dang bal po dang bod rnams
NK041(di)021:74: las byung ba'i lo rgyus rgya cher 'dug pa ni
NK041(di)021:75: yig rnying rnams las shes par bya'o //
NK041(di)021:77: sgrol ma'i dbang dang rjes gnang gang rung thob pa /
NK041(di)021:78: phyag 'tshal nyi shu rtsa gcig gi lung thob cing
NK041(di)021:79: khyad par du tshul 'di'i lung thob pa'i rab dge
NK041(di)021:81: than dge bsnyen yang rung ste /
NK041(di)021:82: khyim pa ma yin pa nyi shu rtsa gcig gam /
NK041(di)021:85: gcig gam gsum la sogs pa yul dus dang 'tshams pas bsgrub bo //
NK041(di)021:86: bzhi pa cho ga dngos la gsum /
NK041(di)021:91: dus bzang po'am dgos pa la bab pa'i tshe /
NK041(di)021:92: gnas khang byi dor byas pa'i gung du stegs bu
NK041(di)021:93: mtho zhing khebs ldan gyi dbus su rdul tshon nam
NK041(di)021:94: ras bris kyi pad+ma 'dab ma nyi shu ba lte
NK041(di)021:96: ma 'byor na man+dala la 'bru'i tshom bu dbus su gcig /
NK041(di)021:97: mtha' bskor phyogs bzhir lnga re ste nyer gcig tshang
NK041(di)021:98: bar bkod pa'i steng du sgrol ma nyer gcig gam
NK041(di)021:99: / sgrol ljang gi sku bris 'bur gang rung rab gnas can bkod /
NK041(di)021:100: de'i mdun du phyi mchod phreng tshar /
NK041(di)021:102: sku phyis na bza' rnams dang /
NK041(di)021:103: snod gtsang mar gtor zlum theb kyu mang pos bskor
NK041(di)021:104: rgyan spros can bcas gtsang sbra dang ldan par bsham
NK041(di)021:105: / de dag las dma' ba'i stegs bur bgegs gtor cog rdog ril bu spungs pa dang /
NK041(di)021:107: ngar chung chang bu ting lo theb kyu bcas pa dang /
NK041(di)021:108: gzhi bdag la dkar gtor 'bru blugs pa bcas bsham mo //
NK041(di)021:110: stegs bu grub bzhi ba'i steng du zan nam 'jim pa'i ri rab bang rim bzhi pa bya /
NK041(di)021:111: ri rab kyi steng du mkhar thabs gru bzhi rgya'i gtog dang bcas pa mdzes tshon byas la bzhag /
NK041(di)021:112: mkhar gyi sgo mdun gyi bang rim gong ma la
NK041(di)021:113: zan gyi ngar mi mtho gang rta la zhon pa
NK041(di)021:114: gcig bzhag / de la gser g.yu dang dar gos kyis brgyan /
NK041(di)021:115: zan la gser skyems brdar ba'i mi'u thung gis gzugs sum cu lag bazo'am /
NK041(di)021:116: spar btab pa gang ba der byas la bang rim dang po mkhar gyi mtha' bskor du bzhag /
NK041(di)021:117: ngar mi che ba rta can gyi g.yas g.yon rgyab gsum du nam mkha' gsum btsug /
NK041(di)021:118: mdun du rgyang bu gsum btsug /
NK041(di)021:119: bang rim gnyis bar zhal zas brgyad dang bya rigs sna tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK041(di)021:120: bang rim gsum bar glang chen rta mdzo ba glang
NK041(di)021:121: ra lug sogs dud 'gro'i rigs kyi gzugs brnyan dang
NK041(di)021:122: / shwa gna' sgo sogs ri dwags kyi rigs thams cad kyi gzugs brnyan dang /
NK041(di)021:123: nya lcong sbal sbrul sogs chu gnas sna tshogs kyi gzugs brnyan bkod /
NK041(di)021:124: bang rim bzhi pa'i phyogs bzhi dang zur bzhir mar me re re ste brgyad /
NK041(di)021:125: 'bru sna tshogs dang zas sna nor g.yu'i rigs gang 'dzom /
NK041(di)021:126: sman sna 'bru sna ngar mi chang bu gos dum spu glud gzugs lhag ma'i rigs dang /
NK041(di)021:127: than ltas sogs byung ba yin na gang byung ba'i
NK041(di)021:128: gzugs brnyan dang yas stag sogs kyi rigs ci 'dzom
NK041(di)021:129: pas bskor / mthar lcags ris bskor ba'i g.yas kyi khar pho tong drug /
NK041(di)021:133: mtshams bzhir rgyang bu bzhi rnams btsug /
NK041(di)021:134: de'i phyi nas snal mas bcings te mdun du mdud pa kha tshur rang la bstan te bzhag go //
NK041(di)021:135: bca' lugs 'di bzhin yig rnying nas bshad pa dang
NK041(di)021:136: dam pa kha cig gi phyag bzhes su snang bas
NK041(di)021:138: spyir gto mdos kyi rigs la mkhas blun dang 'byor
NK041(di)021:139: pa'i khyad par gyis rgyas bsdus 'dra min rang bzo'i
NK041(di)021:140: bya ba mtha' gcig tu ma nges pas 'di la'ang
NK041(di)021:141: byed lugs sna tshogs su snang ngo //
NK041(di)021:150: bdag dang 'gro ba nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i
NK041(di)021:151: sems can dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid byang
NK041(di)021:152: chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du /
NK041(di)021:153: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK041(di)021:154: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK041(di)021:157: rje btsun ma 'phags ma sgrol ma'i lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK041(di)021:159: sems can thams cad kyi don du rnam pa mkhyen pa sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK041(di)021:160: de'i phyir du rje btsun ma 'phags ma sgrol ma'i bsgom bzlas la 'jug par bagyi'o //
NK041(di)021:162: sangs rgyas chos tshogs lan gsum dang /
NK041(di)021:163: sems can thams cad bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang sogs kyis tshad med bzhi bsgom /
NK041(di)021:164: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi snying gar a las zla ba'i steng du t+aam ljang gu /
NK041(di)021:166: rnam smin rdos bcas dang sdig sgrib lhan cig tu sbyangs /
NK041(di)021:167: rang nyid sgrol ma'i skur gyur ba ni /
NK041(di)021:168: sku mdog ljang gu zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas mchog
NK041(di)021:169: sbyin dang g.yon ut+pala sngon po'i rtsa ba thugs kar
NK041(di)021:170: snyan gyi thad kar kha bye ba /
NK041(di)021:171: zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum pa'i skyil krung phyed pa'i rol bas bzhugs pa /
NK041(di)021:172: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK041(di)021:173: pad zla'i gdan la bzhugs par gyur /
NK041(di)021:174: thugs kar zla ba la gnas pa'i t+aam de las 'od zer 'phros /
NK041(di)021:175: rje btsun 'phags ma sgrol ma ye shes sems dpa'i
NK041(di)021:176: lha tshogs badz+ra sa ma dzahphyaga dang mchod pa yid
NK041(di)021:177: kyis bya zhing ngag nas mi brjod /
NK041(di)021:182: thugs kar h'u sngon pos mtshan par gyur /
NK041(di)021:183: lha yi sku'i gsal snang la sems bzung /
NK041(di)021:185: thugs kar zla ba'i steng t+aam yig ljang gu'i mtha'
NK041(di)021:186: bskor du yi ge bcu pas bskor ba bsgoms la
NK041(di)021:187: / t+aa re tut+t+aa re tu re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:189: gzungs sngags kyis bskor ba gsal btabs la /
NK041(di)021:190: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK041(di)021:191: na mo +aar+ya a wa lo ki te shwa r+aa ya /
NK041(di)021:194: ma h+aa ka ru ni k+aa ya /
NK041(di)021:195: t+aa re tut+ta re tu re sarba du dush+ta /
NK041(di)021:204: sarba dush+tam stam b+ha ni ta re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:207: ye shes pa mdun du zhugs par gyur /
NK041(di)021:210: rje btsun ma 'phags ma sgrol mas bdag dang sems
NK041(di)021:211: can thams cad la mchog dang thun mong gi dngos
NK041(di)021:212: grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK041(di)021:216: rang dam tshig pa'i nga rgyal gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK041(di)021:218: shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK041(di)021:219: stong pa'i ngang las pam las sna tshogs pad+ma'i lte
NK041(di)021:220: bar a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du
NK041(di)021:221: t+aam ljang gu las ut+pala t+aam gis mtshan pa yongs
NK041(di)021:222: su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das ma rje btsun
NK041(di)021:223: ma 'phags ma sgrol ma sku mdog ljang gu rin
NK041(di)021:224: po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis spras pa /
NK041(di)021:225: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgyas
NK041(di)021:226: sems can thams cad kyi bsam pa rdzogs par mdzad
NK041(di)021:227: pa / g.yon pas rab tu rgyas pa'i ut+pala 'dzin cing mdzes pa'i dar gyi na bza' bklubs pa /
NK041(di)021:228: rgyal ba don yod grub pa'i dbu rgyan can /
NK041(di)021:229: pad zla'i gdan la rol pa'i stabs kyis sangs rgyas
NK041(di)021:230: dang byang chub sems dpa' dpag tu med pa'i dbus
NK041(di)021:231: su bzhugs pa / mtha' bskor gyi pad 'dab nyi
NK041(di)021:232: shu la mdun nas g.yas bskor gyis rim pa bzhin
NK041(di)021:233: myur zhing dpa' ba bgegs dang 'tshe ba rnam par
NK041(di)021:234: 'joms pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog dmar mo dbang du
NK041(di)021:235: sdud pa'i bum pa dmar po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:236: ston ka'i zla ba ltar dkar ba nad dang gdon
NK041(di)021:237: bgegs 'joms pa'i sgrol ma zhi ba'i bum pa dkar
NK041(di)021:238: po bsnams pa / tshe dang longs spyod 'phel bar
NK041(di)021:239: mdzad pa'i sgrol ma gser mdog can rgyas pa'i bum
NK041(di)021:241: tshe'i mchog stsol bar mdzad pa'i sgrol ma rnam par
NK041(di)021:242: rgyal ma gser mdog can tshe'i bum pa ser po
NK041(di)021:243: bsnams pa / h'u sgra sgrogs ma shes rab kyi
NK041(di)021:244: phyag rgyas dbang du sdud par bya zhing 'gugs par
NK041(di)021:245: mdzad pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog dmar ser yid 'phrog
NK041(di)021:246: pa'i bum pa dmar po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:247: 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba 'byung po
NK041(di)021:248: 'dul bar mdzad pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog dmar nag
NK041(di)021:249: 'byung po ro langs myos por byed pa'i bum pa
NK041(di)021:251: gzhan 'joms shing gzhan gyi rig sngags zlog par mdzad
NK041(di)021:252: pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog nag mo rig sngags zlog
NK041(di)021:253: pa'i bum pa nag po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:254: bdud dgra 'joms pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog dmar nag
NK041(di)021:255: bdud dang dgra 'joms pa'i bum pa dmar po bsnams
NK041(di)021:256: pa / dkon mchog gsum mtshon gyi phyag rgya can
NK041(di)021:257: 'jigs pa thams cad bsrung bar mdzad ma 'jigs pa
NK041(di)021:258: thams cad 'joms pa'i bum pa dkar po bsnams pa
NK041(di)021:259: pa / / bdud dang bar du gcod pa 'dul
NK041(di)021:260: bar mdzad pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog dmar mo bdud
NK041(di)021:261: 'joms pa'i bum pa dmar po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:262: dbul ba'i sdug bsngal sel zhing dngos grub stsol bar
NK041(di)021:263: mdzad pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog gser btso ma ltar
NK041(di)021:264: dmar ser dbul ba sel ba'i bum pa ser po
NK041(di)021:265: bsnams pa / bkra shis thams cad sbyin par mdzad
NK041(di)021:266: ma sku mdog gser gyi mdog can bkra shis pa'i
NK041(di)021:267: bum pa dkar po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:268: bgegs dang bar chad 'joms par mdzad ma me ltar
NK041(di)021:269: 'bar ba'i sku mdog dmar mo bar chad srung ba'i
NK041(di)021:270: bum pa dmar po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:271: bgegs rnam par 'joms pa'i khro gnyer can gyi sgrol
NK041(di)021:272: ma sku mdog nag po khro gnyer cung zad yod
NK041(di)021:273: pa bgegs la bsnun pa'i bum pa mthing ga bsnams
NK041(di)021:274: pa / sdig pa dang sgrib pa sbyong bar mdzad
NK041(di)021:275: pa'i sgrol ma zhi ba chen mo sku mdog dkar
NK041(di)021:276: mo sdig sgrib sbyong bar mdzad pa'i bum pa dkar
NK041(di)021:277: pa / po bsnams pa / pha rol gyi rtsod
NK041(di)021:278: pa las rgyal zhing blo gros 'phel bar mdzad pa'i
NK041(di)021:279: sgrol ma sku mdog dmar mo shes rab 'phel bar
NK041(di)021:280: mdzad pa'i bum pa dmar ser bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:281: bdud dang bar chad zhi zhing 'jig rten gsum g.yo
NK041(di)021:282: ba'i sgrol ma sku mdog dmar ser rig sngags gnon
NK041(di)021:283: pa'i bum pa ser po bsnams /
NK041(di)021:284: klu'i dug thams cad rab tu zhi zhing sel bar
NK041(di)021:285: mdzad pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog dkar mo dug nad
NK041(di)021:286: sel ba'i bum pa dkar po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:287: rmi lam ngan pa dang sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad
NK041(di)021:288: pa'i sgrol ma sku mdog dkar mo sdug bsngal sel
NK041(di)021:289: ba'i bum pa dkar po bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:290: rims nad thams cad sel bar mdzad pa'i sgrol ma
NK041(di)021:291: sku mdog dkar mo rims nad sel ba'i bum pa
NK041(di)021:293: phrin las yongs rdzogs kyi sgrol ma sku mdog dkar
NK041(di)021:294: mo 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro ba dngos grub sna
NK041(di)021:295: tshogs 'byung ba'i bum pa ljang gu bsnams pa /
NK041(di)021:296: thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK041(di)021:297: phyag g.yas mchog sbyin gyi mthil na phrin las so so sgrub pa'i bum pa dang /
NK041(di)021:298: phyag g.yon ut+pala bsnams shing pad zla'i gdan la brkyang bskum stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK041(di)021:299: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan cing 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phro ba /
NK041(di)021:300: mtha' bskor du sangs rgyas byang sems yi dam mkha'
NK041(di)021:301: 'gro chos skyong srung ma'i tshogs dpag tu med pas
NK041(di)021:302: bskor ba / de dag thams cad kyi dpral bar /
NK041(di)021:304: de las 'od zer 'phros pas po ta la nas
NK041(di)021:305: rje btsun 'phags ma sgrol ma nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK041(di)021:306: la sangs rgyas byang sems yi dam mkha' 'gro chos
NK041(di)021:307: skyong dpag tu med pas bskor ba badz+ra sa m+aa
NK041(di)021:308: dza / zhes bsdu ba'i phyag rgya dang /
NK041(di)021:310: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK041(di)021:311: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha //
NK041(di)021:312: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa //
NK041(di)021:313: bcom ldan 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)021:314: po ta la yi gnas mchog nas //
NK041(di)021:315: t+aam yig ljang gu las 'khrungs shing //
NK041(di)021:316: 'od dpag med pas dbu la brgyan //
NK041(di)021:317: dus gsum sangs rgyas phrin las ma //
NK041(di)021:318: 'gro ba'i don phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)021:321: btso ma gser gyi mdog 'dra shing //
NK041(di)021:322: nyi ma las lhag gzi brjid che //
NK041(di)021:323: dad pas spyan ni drangs par bgyi //
NK041(di)021:324: zhi zhing thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK041(di)021:325: dul zhing bsam gtan sa la bzhugs //
NK041(di)021:326: chos dang ye shes chags bral ba //
NK041(di)021:327: kun tu mi bzad nus par ldan //
NK041(di)021:328: tshur spyon tshur spyon zhi dag lha //
NK041(di)021:329: thub pa'i skyes mchog thams cad mkhyen //
NK041(di)021:330: shin tu legs byas gzugs brnyan ni //
NK041(di)021:331: mchod pas 'dir ni gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)021:332: 'dir ni gzugs dang lhan cig tu //
NK041(di)021:333: 'gro ba'i don du bzhugs nas kyang //
NK041(di)021:334: nad med tshe dang dbang phyug dang //
NK041(di)021:335: mchog rnams legs par stsal du gsol //
NK041(di)021:336: zhes pas sangs rgyas byang sems thams cad spyan drangs par mos /
NK041(di)021:337: khrus gsol phyag len ltar byas la /
NK041(di)021:338: khyed kyi rang bzhin yongs dag pas //
NK041(di)021:339: srid pa'i 'ching ba mi mnga' yang //
NK041(di)021:340: bdag cag sgrib pa sbyang slad du //
NK041(di)021:341: gtsang ma chab kyis sku khrus gsol //
NK041(di)021:343: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK041(di)021:344: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar //
NK041(di)021:345: lha yi chu ni dag pa yis //
NK041(di)021:346: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol //
NK041(di)021:347: h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aahk+aa ya bi sho d+ha na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:349: de nas de la kha dog legs bsgyur ba'i //
NK041(di)021:350: na bza' shin tu dri zhim dam pa 'bul //
NK041(di)021:351: gos bzang srab la 'jam mdzes sna tshogs dang //
NK041(di)021:352: rgyan mchog brgya phrag de dang de dag 'bul //
NK041(di)021:353: badz+ra wa stra a lam ka ra p+au dza me
NK041(di)021:354: g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye
NK041(di)021:356: bdag dang 'gro la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK041(di)021:357: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni //
NK041(di)021:358: ji srid mchod pa bdag bgyid na //
NK041(di)021:359: de srid bcom ldan bzhugs su gsol //
NK041(di)021:360: badz+ra +aa sa na pad+ma ka ma l+aa ya s+t+wam /
NK041(di)021:361: +aar+ya t+aa re sa pa ri w+aa ra push+pe pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:365: nee wi d+ya pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:367: lha dang lha min cod pan gyis //
NK041(di)021:369: lag gnyis mnyam pa'i thal mo las gung mo gnyis
NK041(di)021:370: rtse sbyar ba'i tshigs gsum par mdzub mo'i rtse mo
NK041(di)021:371: bkug la bzhag mthe bong gnyis gshib ste mnyam du
NK041(di)021:372: bsgreng / srin mdzub nang du bcug /
NK041(di)021:373: mathe'u chung sbyar nas brkyangs pa ut+pala kha bye ba'i phyag rgya bcings te /
NK041(di)021:374: dzahmh'u bam hoh ye shes pa dang dam tshig pa gnyis med du 'dres par gyur /
NK041(di)021:376: mdun bskyed rje btsun ma gtso 'khor rnams kyi thugs
NK041(di)021:377: kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du t+aam yig
NK041(di)021:378: ljang gu'i mtha' mar yi ge bcu pa'i sngags kyis
NK041(di)021:380: bdag gzhan sems can thams cad kyi 'jigs pa brgyad
NK041(di)021:381: dang bcu drug sogs mi mthun pa'i phyogs zhi nas
NK041(di)021:382: tshe dang bsod nams dpal 'byor 'dod dgu mtha' dag
NK041(di)021:385: t+aa re tut+t+aa re tu re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:386: rtsa sngags ji ltar 'os pa longs skabs dang bstun te bazla'o //
NK041(di)021:387: gsum pa mchod bstod gtor 'bul sogs lan gsum bya dgos pa'i thog mar mchod pa byin rlabs ni /
NK041(di)021:388: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi byin
NK041(di)021:389: gyis brlabs pa'i stobs dang bdag gi bsod nams dang
NK041(di)021:391: rig sngags kyi stobs kyis sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK041(di)021:392: sems dpa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor rnams la mchog tu
NK041(di)021:393: rgya chen po byang chub sems dpa'i kun tu bzang
NK041(di)021:394: po'i spyod pa las mngon par mtho ba'i mchod pa'i
NK041(di)021:395: sprin chen po rab tu 'phro bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:397: na mahsarba bud+d+ha bo d+h+ai sa t+wa n+aam sarba th+aa
NK041(di)021:398: kham ung+ga te s+pha ra na i mam ga ga
NK041(di)021:399: na kham sa man+ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:400: zhes sngags lan brgyad brjod la /
NK041(di)021:401: 'jig rten khams ni dpag med na //
NK041(di)021:402: mchod yon ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK041(di)021:403: bdag gis gus par bshams pa ni //
NK041(di)021:404: rgyal ba'i yum la mchod par bgyi //
NK041(di)021:405: +aar+ya t+aa re sa pa ri wa ra ar+g+ham pra
NK041(di)021:406: t+aits+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra
NK041(di)021:408: tshigs bcad dang sngags kyi thog mtha' 'dra ba la /
NK041(di)021:419: yid 'ong khang brtsegs khrus kyi rdzing //
NK041(di)021:420: skyed mos tshal dang rin chen bdun //
NK041(di)021:421: khri stan 'phan gdugs rgyal mtshan sogs //
NK041(di)021:422: nam mkha'i khams kun bkang ste 'bul //
NK041(di)021:423: sarba bi shish+tha p+au dza me g+ha pra sa ra sa mu dre +aahmh'u /
NK041(di)021:425: bcom ldan 'das ma gtso 'khor gyi phyag g.yas skyabs
NK041(di)021:426: sbyin mdzad pa'i 'og tu bsrung bya 'khor bcas tshud
NK041(di)021:427: bar bsams la / rje btsun ma 'phags ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)021:428: phyag 'tshal t+aa re myur ma dpa' mo /
NK041(di)021:429: tut+t+aa ra yis 'jigs pa kun sel /
NK041(di)021:430: tu res don kun grub pa'i sgrol ma /
NK041(di)021:431: s+w+aa h+aa'i yi ger bcas la rab 'dud /
NK041(di)021:432: phyag 'tshal sgrol ma myur ma dpa' mo /
NK041(di)021:434: phyag 'tshal ba ni nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK041(di)021:437: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK041(di)021:438: mchod rdzas ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK041(di)021:439: bdag gis gus pas bshams pa 'di //
NK041(di)021:440: rgyal ba'i yum la mchod par bgyi //
NK041(di)021:441: +aar+ya t+aa re sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham p+aa
NK041(di)021:442: d+yam push+pe d+hu pe +aa lo ke gan+d+he nee bi
NK041(di)021:443: d+ya shab+ta pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sa mu
NK041(di)021:444: dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK041(di)021:446: sngar bzhin phyag 'tshal nyer gcig tshar gcig brjod /
NK041(di)021:447: de lta bu'i mchod bstod lan bdun rdzogs nas /
NK041(di)021:448: lha mo la gus yang dag ldan pas /
NK041(di)021:449: sogs phan yon tshar gcig brjod /
NK041(di)021:450: de nas gtor ma cha gsum gyi dang po sgrol ma gtso 'khor la 'bul ba ni /
NK041(di)021:452: gtor ma'i steng du a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK041(di)021:453: la gnas pa'i t+aam ljang gu de las 'od zer
NK041(di)021:454: 'phros pas sems can gyi don byas nas tshur 'dus
NK041(di)021:455: / snod la thim pas yangs shing rgya che ba dang /
NK041(di)021:456: bcud la thim pas lha rdzas kyi gtor ma bdud rtsir gyur par bsam /
NK041(di)021:458: lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK041(di)021:459: mdun bskyed kyi bcom ldan 'das ma 'khor bcas kyi
NK041(di)021:460: ljags 'od zer gyi sbu gu can gyis gtor ma
NK041(di)021:462: t+aa re tut+ta re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:463: a ka ro sogs btags pa lan bdun nam nyer gcig gis phul la /
NK041(di)021:464: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma 'dod yon ma tshang ba
NK041(di)021:465: med pa dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i gtor ma zag med
NK041(di)021:466: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po 'dzad
NK041(di)021:467: pa med pa 'di nyid rtsa ba dang brgyud par
NK041(di)021:468: bcas pa'i dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams dang
NK041(di)021:469: / rje btsun ma 'phags ma sgrol ma thugs rje'i
NK041(di)021:470: bdag nyid can nyi shu rtsa gcig la sogs pa
NK041(di)021:471: yi dam rgyud sde bzhi dang theg pa rim dgu'i
NK041(di)021:473: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK041(di)021:474: bstan pa dang 'khor rnam bzhi skyong bar zhal gyis
NK041(di)021:475: bzhes pa'i phyi nang gi dam can chos skyong srung
NK041(di)021:476: ma'i tshogs ma lus pa rnams dang /
NK041(di)021:477: nor lha gter bdag dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul bar bagyi'o //
NK041(di)021:478: bzhes nas rkyen phyi nang gi bar chad thams cad nye bar zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK041(di)021:479: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa'i don thams cad chos
NK041(di)021:480: dang mthun pa'i yid bzhin du 'grub par mdzad du
NK041(di)021:481: gsol / bdag sogs sems can thams cad kyi rgyud
NK041(di)021:482: la tshogs gnyis rdzogs sgrib gnyis byang nas myur du
NK041(di)021:483: sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par mdzad du gsol
NK041(di)021:485: bdag gis bsam pa'i stobs dag dang //
NK041(di)021:486: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyin stobs dang //
NK041(di)021:487: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs rnams kyis //
NK041(di)021:488: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //
NK041(di)021:489: de dag thams cad ci rigs pa //
NK041(di)021:491: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:492: ces brjod rol mo dang bcas pas gtor ma dang po rten gyi drung du phul la /
NK041(di)021:493: rje btsun 'phags ma sgrol ma dang /
NK041(di)021:495: kun nas dang bas phyag bagyi'o //
NK041(di)021:496: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK041(di)021:497: pra na me na badz+ra b+han+d+ha nam ka ro mi
NK041(di)021:499: me tog bdug spos mar me dri /
NK041(di)021:501: 'phags ma'i tshogs kyis bzhes su gsol /
NK041(di)021:504: nee wi d+ya'i bar nyer spyod lnga dang /
NK041(di)021:505: sarba bi shi sh+tha p+au dza me g+ha pra sa ra sa mu dre +aahmh'u /
NK041(di)021:506: gis 'phan gdugs rgyal mtshan rin chen sna bdun la sogs pas mchod pa'i rjes su /
NK041(di)021:507: thog ma med nas da lta'i bar /
NK041(di)021:509: 'dren pa'i dpal du bdag gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:511: rje btsun bcom ldan 'das ma thugs rje can //
NK041(di)021:513: skabs 'dir rang lugs kyi chos skyong gtor 'bul byed
NK041(di)021:514: par 'dod na'ang rgyas bsdus gang 'grub bya bar gsungs
NK041(di)021:516: ma byas kyang gzhung gi dngos don min pas do gal med do //
NK041(di)021:517: gang ltar gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK041(di)021:518: thal mo spyi bor sbyar te yid brtan pa'i sgo nas tshigs 'di dag brjod do //
NK041(di)021:520: 'phags pa dkon mchog gsum gyi mthu dang /
NK041(di)021:521: gsang sngags gzugs sngags rig sngags kyi mthu dang /
NK041(di)021:522: yi dam zhi ba khro bo rnams kyi mthu dang /
NK041(di)021:523: khyad par du 'phags ma sgrol ma thugs rje'i bdag nyid can nyi shu rtsa gcig gi mthu dang /
NK041(di)021:524: bstan pa rin po che bsrung zhing skyong bar zhal
NK041(di)021:525: gyis bzhes pa'i dam can chos skyong srung ma rnams
NK041(di)021:526: kyi mthu dang / chos nyid rnam par dag cing
NK041(di)021:527: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i mthu dang
NK041(di)021:528: kyi mthu dang / / bdag gis gtan pa med
NK041(di)021:529: pa'i mchod sbyin rgya chen po bgyis pa'i mthu stobs
NK041(di)021:532: grul bum dang dri za dang sha zas dang /
NK041(di)021:533: srul po dang smyo byed dang brjed byed dang /
NK041(di)021:534: de dag rgan po dang rgan mo dang /
NK041(di)021:535: de dag gi bu pho dang bu mo dang /
NK041(di)021:538: gzhan yang ma mo mkha' 'gro dang /
NK041(di)021:540: gshin rje dang rgyal po dang /
NK041(di)021:546: 'byung po thams cad dang btsan bdud rnams dang /
NK041(di)021:548: drang srong dang rig sngags 'chang ba thams cad dang /
NK041(di)021:554: za ma la sogs pa thams cad dang /
NK041(di)021:555: gdon bgegs chen po'i rigs thams cad kyi sbyor ba
NK041(di)021:556: ngan pas gnod pa'i las byed pa'i bsam sbyor ngan
NK041(di)021:557: pa thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:560: phyin chad mi byed par dam chos shig /
NK041(di)021:561: de'i phyir so so'i 'dod yon rnams kyang ster ro //
NK041(di)021:563: bdag cag dpon slob rgyu sbyor ba la /
NK041(di)021:564: mi nad dang phyugs nad dang /
NK041(di)021:569: phur ka dang gtad khrom dang /
NK041(di)021:586: dur sri dang god kha dang god sri dang /
NK041(di)021:590: bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad dang /
NK041(di)021:591: dus ma yin par 'chi ba dang /
NK041(di)021:592: nor dang longs spyod mi 'phel bar byed pa dang /
NK041(di)021:593: bkra mi shis par byed pa thams cad dang /
NK041(di)021:594: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa'i lus ngag yid gsum
NK041(di)021:595: la gnod par byed pa'i nad rigs gdon bgegs bar
NK041(di)021:597: dgra 'dre byur gsum gyi gnod pa thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:600: phyin chad mi 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:601: thal mo brdab la rol mo drag tu bya ba'i mthar /
NK041(di)021:602: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK041(di)021:603: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi byin gyis rlabs kyi stobs dang /
NK041(di)021:604: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' thang chen po dang /
NK041(di)021:605: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing /
NK041(di)021:606: chos nyid rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i stobs kyis de de bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:608: des mchod bstod dang gtor ma cha dang po grub /
NK041(di)021:609: gnyis pa la slar yang mchod pa kha gso /
NK041(di)021:611: tshar dang po la rgyas pa dang /
NK041(di)021:612: phyi ma rnams la mchod tshig bsdus pa'i mchod pa /
NK041(di)021:613: phyag 'tshal nyer gcig gi bstod pa spel ba lan bdun gyi mthar phan yon bcas grub nas /
NK041(di)021:614: gtor ma gnyis pa'ang 'bru gsum gyi byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK041(di)021:615: +aa k+aa ro sogs lan bdun brjod pa'i rjes su /
NK041(di)021:616: rang rang gi yid dang mthun pa'i gtor ma 'dod
NK041(di)021:617: yon phun sum tshogs pa thams cad nam mkha' mdzod
NK041(di)021:618: bzhin du 'dzad pa med pa 'di nyid bgegs rigs
NK041(di)021:620: byis pa'i gdon chen bco lnga /
NK041(di)021:621: nad bdag yams bdag gdon bgegs 'byung po'i rigs su
NK041(di)021:622: gyur pa thams cad dang 'gro ba rigs drug lam
NK041(di)021:623: rgyud lnga skye gnas bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can thams
NK041(di)021:625: so so'i bsam pa dang mthun pa'i longs spyod zad
NK041(di)021:626: mi shes pa ji srid 'khor ba ma stongs kyi
NK041(di)021:627: bar du 'byung zhing rgyas par gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:628: thams cad sdug bsngal las thar nas rnam pa thams
NK041(di)021:629: cad mkhyen pa sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po
NK041(di)021:630: che'i myur du thob pa'i skal ba dang ldan par
NK041(di)021:631: gyur cig / thams cad nam mkha' mdzod bzhin du //
NK041(di)021:632: longs spyod zad pa med par shog /
NK041(di)021:633: rtsod pa med cing 'tshe med par //
NK041(di)021:634: rang dbang du ni spyod par shog /
NK041(di)021:636: bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs dag dang //
NK041(di)021:638: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:639: zhes pa'i bar gong bzhin brjod la gtor ma mdos nang phul ba rol mo bya /
NK041(di)021:640: de nas thal mo mgrin pa'i thad du sbyar la /
NK041(di)021:642: 'phags pa dkon mchog gsum gyi mthu dang /
NK041(di)021:643: sogs nas thal mo brdab nas rol mo bya ba dang /
NK041(di)021:644: de bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:645: ces pa'i bar gong bzhin brjod do //
NK041(di)021:646: des mchod bstod gtor ma cha gnyis pa grub /
NK041(di)021:647: gsum pa la yang mchod pa kha gso /
NK041(di)021:648: byin rlabs nas mchod bstod rgyas bsdus 'don lugs snga
NK041(di)021:649: ma bzhin tshar bdun phan yon dang bcas pa song
NK041(di)021:650: nas / gtor ma gsum pa 'bru gsum gyis byin brlab /
NK041(di)021:651: a k+aa ro sogs lan gsum gyis bsngosa nas /
NK041(di)021:652: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma gzugs sgra dri ro reg
NK041(di)021:653: bya phun sum tshogs pa so so'i yid dang mthun
NK041(di)021:654: pa'i longs spyod zag pa med pa 'di nyid bdag
NK041(di)021:655: cag dpon slob yon mchod 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK041(di)021:656: kyi tshe rabs 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas
NK041(di)021:657: tha ma da lta la thug gi bar du nyon
NK041(di)021:658: mongs pa dug gsum dang dug lnga'i dbang gis brkus
NK041(di)021:659: shing 'phrog pas nor dbul ba'i lan chags /
NK041(di)021:660: brdung zhing brtsogs pas nad dang 'tshe ba'i lan chags /
NK041(di)021:661: bsad cing gtub pa srog bcad pas tshe thung ba'i lan chags /
NK041(di)021:662: mtho ba'i mkhar phab pa dma' ba'i yul bcom pa /
NK041(di)021:664: sngon gyi lan chags pa la sogs pa'i lan chags
NK041(di)021:665: dang sha 'khon gyi bdag po bdag mo thams cad
NK041(di)021:666: la sbyin no // gnod byed gdon bgegs lan chags
NK041(di)021:667: kyi rigs su gyur pa thams cad tshims par gyur
NK041(di)021:668: la sbyin no // cig / ngoms par gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:669: tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas bsags pa'i lan chags thams cad byang bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:670: bu lon sod par gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:671: sha mkhon dang phog thugs su gyur pa thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:672: bsam ngan dang gnod sems gdug rtsub thams cad dang bral nas /
NK041(di)021:673: phan pa dang zhi ba dang byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:674: mthar thug rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin
NK041(di)021:675: po che myur du thob pa'i skal ba dang ldan
NK041(di)021:676: par gyur cig / thams cad nam mkha' mdzod bzhin du //
NK041(di)021:679: bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs dag dang //
NK041(di)021:680: sogs gong ltar du brjod pas /
NK041(di)021:681: rol mo dang bcas pas gtor ma mdos nang du phul lo //
NK041(di)021:682: de nas thal mo snying gar sbyar la yid brtan pa'i ngang nas /
NK041(di)021:684: 'phags pa dkon mchog gsum gyi mthu dang /
NK041(di)021:685: sogs nas thal mo brdeb pa rol mo bcas /
NK041(di)021:686: de de bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:687: bar tshang bar brjod pas cha gsum pa grub /
NK041(di)021:688: gtor ma bzhi pa bzhi bdag dkar gtor mdos kyi lam sel gyi tshul du bsngo ba yin pas /
NK041(di)021:689: spro na gser skyems dkar gtor spyi 'gro rgyas pa skabs 'dir sbyar chog /
NK041(di)021:690: bsdu na 'bru gsum gyis byin brlab /
NK041(di)021:691: a k+aa ro lan gsum gyis bsngo /
NK041(di)021:692: sdig pa ci yang mi bya zhing //
NK041(di)021:694: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya chen po 'di gnas
NK041(di)021:695: bdag gzhi bdag yul bdag grong bdag gnyug mar gnas
NK041(di)021:697: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar ba dang /
NK041(di)021:698: 'jig rten du dge legs rgya chen po 'byung zhing /
NK041(di)021:699: bdag cag dpon slob sbyin bdag 'khor bcas kyi 'gal
NK041(di)021:700: rkyen bar chad thams cad zhi zhing bsam sbyor chos
NK041(di)021:701: mthun yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i sdong grogs mdzod cig
NK041(di)021:702: / ces pa tsam brjod la mdos phul phyogs su bskyal bas 'thus so //
NK041(di)021:703: bzhi pa mdos klud snang srid la bardzanga zhing bsngo ba la /
NK041(di)021:704: thog mar sngags drug phyag drug gis byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK041(di)021:705: mdos chu gtsang gis bran la /
NK041(di)021:706: bdag nyid bcom ldan sh+aakya thub //
NK041(di)021:707: phyag rgya'i yi ge a dkar las //
NK041(di)021:709: dri ma sbyongs nas stong bar gyur //
NK041(di)021:710: thal mo khong stong sbyar la /
NK041(di)021:712: lan gsum re re bzhin phyag rgya bkrol nas se gol gtogs pa gzhan rnams la'ang 'gre /
NK041(di)021:713: chos dbyings rnam dag phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)021:714: ting 'dzin bden pas gtor rdzas kyi //
NK041(di)021:715: 'bag rtsog nyams grib nyes skyon dang //
NK041(di)021:716: mtshan 'dzin dri ma dag gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:717: bdag nyid bcom ldan rnam snang mdzad //
NK041(di)021:718: phyag rgya'i yi ge kham sngon las //
NK041(di)021:720: nam mkha'i khams kun khyab par gyur /
NK041(di)021:721: thal mo sbubs stong du sbyar ba'i tshigs par pa
NK041(di)021:722: rnams bcag pa rin chen sgrom bu'i phyag rgya smin
NK041(di)021:724: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK041(di)021:725: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ung+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK041(di)021:726: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:727: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)021:728: ting 'dzin bden rdzas ye shes kyi //
NK041(di)021:729: bskal pa'i bar du zad mi shes //
NK041(di)021:730: rgya che nam mkha' gang gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:731: bdag nyid bcom ldan bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK041(di)021:732: phyag rgya'i yi ge h+r+aihdamara las //
NK041(di)021:734: bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin gyur //
NK041(di)021:736: sor mo gzhan rnams gshog pa ltar gdengs pa bzhi kha'i thad du bzhag la /
NK041(di)021:737: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK041(di)021:738: bdud rtsi thabs sbyor phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)021:739: ting 'dzin bden pas gtor rdzas rnams //
NK041(di)021:740: bdud rtsi ye shes lnga yi dngos //
NK041(di)021:741: 'chi gsos dug lnga'i sman gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:742: bdag nyid bcom ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK041(di)021:743: phyag rgya'i yi ge tram ser las //
NK041(di)021:745: so so'i mos pa ji bzhin gyur //
NK041(di)021:746: lag pa gnyis mdzub mo sgrengs ba'i khu tshur g.yon snying gar bzhag /
NK041(di)021:747: g.yas brkyangs te rdzas la gtod pa'i tshul byas la /
NK041(di)021:748: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta a ba lo ki te sam+b+ha ra sam+b+ha ra h+aum /
NK041(di)021:749: rgya chen shugs ldan phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)021:750: ting 'dzin bden pas gtor rdzas rnams //
NK041(di)021:751: dbang po'i spyod yul tshims byed pa'i //
NK041(di)021:753: bdag nyid bcom ldan don yod grub //
NK041(di)021:754: phyag rgya'i yi ge ha ljang las //
NK041(di)021:756: 'thab rtsod med par thob par gyur //
NK041(di)021:757: lag g.yas rdo rje khu tshur snying gar bcang /
NK041(di)021:758: g.yon pas mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgyas snod 'degs pa'i tshul byas la /
NK041(di)021:759: dz+ny+aa na a ba lo ki te sam+ta s+pha ra
NK041(di)021:760: na rasmi b+ha ba sa ma ya ma h+aa ma
NK041(di)021:761: ni du ru du ru hri da ya dz+wa la
NK041(di)021:762: ni h'u / 'di go ldog pa'ang snang /
NK041(di)021:764: ye shes skar mad'i phyag rgya sngags /
NK041(di)021:765: ting 'dzin ldan pas mgron rnams kun //
NK041(di)021:766: pham rgyal 'khrugs rtsod med par thob //
NK041(di)021:767: dgyes shing re ba gang gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:768: bdag nyid bcom ldan rdo rje 'dzin //
NK041(di)021:769: phyag rgya'i yi ge dza dmar las //
NK041(di)021:771: phrin las gang 'dod sgrub par gyur //
NK041(di)021:772: lag gnyis sor mo bsnol ba'i khu tshur ngos mthe
NK041(di)021:773: bong gnyis gshibs te brkyang ba spyi bor bskor te
NK041(di)021:774: / na mahs man+ta bud+d+hahn+aam gra he shwa ri pra
NK041(di)021:775: b+h+ya dz+yoo te na ma h+aa sa ma ye s+w+aa
NK041(di)021:776: / h+aa / dbang sgyur 'khor lo'i phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)021:777: ting 'dzin bden pas mgron rigs kun //
NK041(di)021:778: bdag gi dbang 'dus gang bcol las //
NK041(di)021:779: sgrub pa'i sdong grogs mdzad gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:782: bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs dag dang //
NK041(di)021:783: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyin stobs dang //
NK041(di)021:784: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs rnams kyis //
NK041(di)021:785: lan chags mgron rnams barngana pa dang //
NK041(di)021:786: sems can kun la phan gdags slad //
NK041(di)021:787: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //
NK041(di)021:788: de dag thams cad ci rigs pa //
NK041(di)021:789: 'jig rten khams ni ma lus pa //
NK041(di)021:790: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:791: ces bden pa'i stobs kyis kyang byin gyis brlab /
NK041(di)021:792: bye brag dmigs pa'i khyad par dbye zhing bsngo ba ni /
NK041(di)021:795: mdun du rin po che las grub pa'i ri rab
NK041(di)021:796: bang rim bzhi pa'i dbus su khang bzang lcags ris
NK041(di)021:797: bskor ba'i mtha' bskor dang ri rab bang rim gyi
NK041(di)021:798: steng rnams su mgron rnams so sor mnyes pa'i mthun
NK041(di)021:799: rdzas 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yi longs spyod 'dzad
NK041(di)021:800: pa med pa sa dang nam mkha' bar snang khyab
NK041(di)021:802: sam+b+ha ra'i sngags lan bdun dang /
NK041(di)021:803: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rgyal ba rin chen mang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)021:804: de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs mdzes dam pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)021:805: de bzhin gshegs pa sku 'byams klas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)021:806: de bzhin gshegs pa 'jigs pa thams cad yongs su bral ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)021:807: gsang sngags 'di yi mthu dang de bzhin gshegs pa khyed rnams kyi mtshan nas brjod cing /
NK041(di)021:808: phyag 'tshal ba'i byin rlabs la brten nas bdag gis
NK041(di)021:809: gtan pa med pa'i mdos gtor rgya chen po bgyis
NK041(di)021:810: pa 'di'i mthus mgron rigs thams cad tshims shing mgu
NK041(di)021:811: nas bdag gzhan gyi bsam pa'i don thams cad chos
NK041(di)021:812: dang mthun pa yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig
NK041(di)021:813: / de nas skabs 'dir yi dam drag po bskyed par bshad pas /
NK041(di)021:814: bdag nyid skad cig gis bcom ldan 'das pad+ma dbang
NK041(di)021:815: chen sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK041(di)021:816: / phyag g.yas pas seng ldeng gi dbyug to nam mkha' la phyar zhing /
NK041(di)021:817: g.yon thugs kar bsdig mdzub mdzad pa /
NK041(di)021:818: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum gdong mig tu bgrad cing /
NK041(di)021:819: zhal nas mche ba bzhi rnam par gtsigs pa /
NK041(di)021:820: smin ma dang sma ra dmar ser dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar ba /
NK041(di)021:821: dbu skra kham ser gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK041(di)021:822: spyi gtsug na rta mgo ljang gu rta skad 'byin pa /
NK041(di)021:823: klu chen po brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK041(di)021:824: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can /
NK041(di)021:825: zhabs g.yas bskum g.yon brkyangs pas ye shes kyi me
NK041(di)021:826: rab tu 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na bzhugs nas gnod
NK041(di)021:828: sdig sgrib thams cad sreg par byed pa che btsan 'gran zla dang bral ba'i skur gyur /
NK041(di)021:829: mdun bskyed sgrol ma 'khor bcas kyang gzu dang dpang la bzhugs nas /
NK041(di)021:830: bdag gis ji ltar bsngosa shing zlog sgyur brjod pa'i
NK041(di)021:831: phrin las mdzad pas mgron thams cad kyis bka' nyan
NK041(di)021:832: cing phrin las myur du sgrub bar gyur /
NK041(di)021:833: ces pa'i nga rgyal ma bral bar rol mo dbyangs dang bcas te 'di skad do //
NK041(di)021:835: gson cig dgongs shig thams cad nyon //
NK041(di)021:836: rtsa brgyud bla ma thams cad kyis //
NK041(di)021:837: do nub bzlog sgyur mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)021:838: yi dam lha tshogs thams cad kyis //
NK041(di)021:839: do nub bzlog sgyur mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)021:840: rje btsun 'phags ma sgrol ma kun //
NK041(di)021:841: do nub bzlog sgyur mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)021:842: ngan par gyur pa thams cad kun //
NK041(di)021:843: myur du bzlog cing med par mdzod //
NK041(di)021:844: dam can chos skyong srung ma rnams //
NK041(di)021:845: 'dir ni bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK041(di)021:846: mdos gtor mchod sbyin glud dang bcas //
NK041(di)021:847: 'di rnams khyer la gnod ma byed //
NK041(di)021:848: snang srid lha 'dre sde brgyad sogs //
NK041(di)021:849: sngags 'chang bdag gi ngag la nyon //
NK041(di)021:850: gzhan gyis rbad la ma nyan cig /
NK041(di)021:851: gdon bgegs chen po khyod rnams kyi //
NK041(di)021:852: bsam sbyor ngan pa zhi bar gyis //
NK041(di)021:853: khyod la dgos pa'i gtor ma dang //
NK041(di)021:854: srog chags nor glud mang po dang //
NK041(di)021:855: la rdzas lung rdzas 'dod gur bcas //
NK041(di)021:856: yid 'ong khang pa spe'u zhol dang //
NK041(di)021:857: yid 'ong rta pho che mgyogs la //
NK041(di)021:858: 'bru yi ngar mi chen po bskyon //
NK041(di)021:859: lus la gser g.yu'i rgyan cha btags //
NK041(di)021:860: rgyan cha yid 'ong si li li //
NK041(di)021:861: dar gyi gos gyon lhubs se lhub //
NK041(di)021:862: smra ba mkhas shing bzhin mdangs rgyas //
NK041(di)021:863: 'og na rta zhon zhungs se zhung //
NK041(di)021:864: mgo la thod bcings pu ru ru //
NK041(di)021:865: rtsed 'jo sna tshogs bsgyur la mkhas //
NK041(di)021:866: g.yu yi lhwam chung zu lu lu //
NK041(di)021:867: gser gyi sked chings khru lu lu //
NK041(di)021:868: nam rgyang ldem pas sku la brgyan //
NK041(di)021:869: pho tong mo tang mi skad smra //
NK041(di)021:870: mnga' ris 'dod rgu tshang ba rnams //
NK041(di)021:871: yon bdag glud du khyod la 'bul //
NK041(di)021:872: yid 'ong nor ni mang po der //
NK041(di)021:873: zhal zas zhim dgu mngar bcu dang //
NK041(di)021:874: 'khor g.yog ngar mi sum cu dang //
NK041(di)021:875: sman spos sgron me gsal ba rnams //
NK041(di)021:876: khyed la mchod pa 'bul lags kyis //
NK041(di)021:877: dwang ba'i sems kyis bzhes nas su //
NK041(di)021:878: sngags pas phur bu bsgril ba dang //
NK041(di)021:879: yungs kar thun du brab pa dang //
NK041(di)021:880: zor kha sna tshogs 'phen pa dang //
NK041(di)021:881: mnan gtad sbyor ba byed pa rnams //
NK041(di)021:882: de dag nus pa phyir la bzlog /
NK041(di)021:883: bon pos rnga chen brdung ba dang //
NK041(di)021:885: rtsod bsdig byed pa phyir la zlog /
NK041(di)021:886: drag sngags phra men byed pa dang //
NK041(di)021:887: sde brgyad drag pos bskul ba rnams //
NK041(di)021:888: de dag nus pa phyir la bzlog /
NK041(di)021:889: chos skyong lha 'dre thams cad kyang //
NK041(di)021:890: la la dkor gyi shul du 'brangs //
NK041(di)021:891: la la mna' zan gshed du 'ong //
NK041(di)021:892: la la sngags pa drag pos rbad //
NK041(di)021:893: la las ston pa'i rgyu 'bras ston //
NK041(di)021:894: la las rims nad dal yams gtong //
NK041(di)021:895: char pa mi 'bebs lo nyes gtong //
NK041(di)021:896: 'ga' zhig sad dang ser ba gtong //
NK041(di)021:897: lan chags bu lon 'debs pa dang //
NK041(di)021:899: mdze nad gtong ba'i klu rnams dang //
NK041(di)021:900: gnod byed lan chags lha 'dre rnams //
NK041(di)021:901: sha khrag srog dbugs za ba dang /
NK041(di)021:902: 'bras bu lo thog za ba dang //
NK041(di)021:903: ngar snabs mi gtsang za ba dang //
NK041(di)021:904: 'byung ba'i lha dang sa bdag dang //
NK041(di)021:905: lo dang spar kha sme bar bcas //
NK041(di)021:906: kun kyang glud kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:907: gnod 'gal ngan pa zhi bar mdzod //
NK041(di)021:908: bu lon lan chags dag par bcol //
NK041(di)021:909: bdag cag longs spyod 'phel bar mdzod //
NK041(di)021:910: rbod gtong byad kha zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:911: bsam pa'i don rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK041(di)021:912: snying rje'i stobs kyis dam chos bshad //
NK041(di)021:914: da ni byang sems ldan par gyis //
NK041(di)021:915: rang gi lus la dpe longs la //
NK041(di)021:916: gzhan la gnod pa ma skyel bar //
NK041(di)021:917: sdig spangs thar pa'i lam la snyoms //
NK041(di)021:918: rang sems chos sku'i rang zhal la //
NK041(di)021:919: 'dzin med yengs med rgyun du ltos //
NK041(di)021:920: stong nyid snying rje'i ngang nyid la //
NK041(di)021:921: nad dang dal yams zhi bar mdzod //
NK041(di)021:922: lo legs char chu dus su phob //
NK041(di)021:924: snga dgra sdang dang da dgra rtsub //
NK041(di)021:925: phyi dgra shom pa thams cad zlog /
NK041(di)021:926: glo bur brgyad cu rtsa gcig zlog /
NK041(di)021:927: ye 'drog sum brgya drug cu zlog /
NK041(di)021:928: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams zlog /
NK041(di)021:929: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams zlog /
NK041(di)021:930: ya bdud g.yos dang dam sri longs //
NK041(di)021:931: ma bdud ma tshan rgyab 'dre dang //
NK041(di)021:932: ma bu'i byur 'dre bzlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:933: sdang ba'i dgra dang gnod pa'i bgegs //
NK041(di)021:934: thams cad ma lus zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:935: lo zla zhag dus ngan pa zlog /
NK041(di)021:936: phung 'dre thams cad zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:937: ltog 'dre thams cad zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:938: sri la rku ba zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:939: byis pa'i gdon rnams zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:940: phyugs kyi gdon rnams zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:941: mi kha kha smras ma gtong zhig /
NK041(di)021:942: gzhan gyi g.yul ngo zhi ba dang //
NK041(di)021:943: bdag gi dmag thabs legs par mdzod //
NK041(di)021:944: dgra jag chom rkun zhi bar mdzod //
NK041(di)021:945: myos shing 'thab pa bsam pa dang //
NK041(di)021:946: nyin gcig gnyis gsum bdun pa yi //
NK041(di)021:947: rims nad thams cad zhi bar mdzod //
NK041(di)021:948: nyam nga 'tshe ba zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:949: ngan dang rtsub pa'i rigs rnams kun //
NK041(di)021:950: da lta nyid du zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:951: yul phyogs dge bar mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)021:952: dam chos rgyas par mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)021:953: 'thab rtsod zhi bar lo brgya 'tsho bar ston brgya mthong bar mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)021:954: bkra shis ri bo brtan pa dang //
NK041(di)021:955: bsod nams nam mkha' nyi 'od dang //
NK041(di)021:956: mi phyed mi shigs dngos grub stsol //
NK041(di)021:957: zhes brjod pas lam du bskyal bcol la /
NK041(di)021:958: rang gis nang nas 'og tu bshad pa'i bden stobs brjod /
NK041(di)021:959: zlog pa 'di tshar grangs gsum sogs bskyar 'dod na'ang bya chog /
NK041(di)021:960: yang na rims gcod pa sogs gal che dus phyi
NK041(di)021:961: rol du gto skyeel byed na 'phen phyogs su dar
NK041(di)021:962: nag dang rol mo bcas te khyer /
NK041(di)021:963: de'ang nad yams dal phyogs lam mdo sogs //
NK041(di)021:964: byad kha dang dgra bgegs la de phyogs /
NK041(di)021:965: than chen char 'bebs la chu mago'am mtsho 'gram du skyel ba sogs rigs pas dpyad /
NK041(di)021:966: mdos gtor gnam du btegs la rang nyid yi dam gyi nga rgyal brtan pa dang /
NK041(di)021:967: sgrol ma sogs kyi gzugs dpang dang rgyab brten gsal
NK041(di)021:968: ba'i ngang nas bden stobs brjod cing mdos bzlog bya
NK041(di)021:970: 'phags pa dkon ma chog gsum gyi mthu dang sogs nas /
NK041(di)021:971: phyin chad mi 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:972: bar gong ltar brjod pa'i mthar /
NK041(di)021:973: sngags pas phur bu bsgril ba dang /
NK041(di)021:974: yungs kar thun du brab pa dang /
NK041(di)021:975: zor kha gnan gtad byed pa dang /
NK041(di)021:976: de dag gi nus mthu thams cad phyir bzlog tu gsol /
NK041(di)021:977: bon pos rnga chen brdung ba dang /
NK041(di)021:980: drag sngags phra men byed pa dang /
NK041(di)021:981: sde brgyad dregs pa bskul ba dang /
NK041(di)021:982: de dag gi nus mthu thams cad phyir bzlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:983: chos skyong dang lha 'dre rnams dkor gyi shul du phreng ba dang /
NK041(di)021:985: sngags pa drag pos rbad pa /
NK041(di)021:987: rims nad yams nad gtong ba /
NK041(di)021:988: char med than chen gtong ba /
NK041(di)021:989: lo nyes btsa' dang sad ser gtong ba /
NK041(di)021:990: lan chags bu lon snyags pa /
NK041(di)021:991: nye 'brel dang grogs kyi shul du 'brang ba /
NK041(di)021:992: klu nad dang mdze nad dang shu ba gtong ba /
NK041(di)021:993: de dag gi nus mthu thams cad phyir bzlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:997: lo zla zhag dus kyi kag rtsub pa /
NK041(di)021:998: spar kha dang sme ba rtsub pa /
NK041(di)021:999: lus kha rje dbang thang zhan pa /
NK041(di)021:1000: bla gnas dang klung rta rgud pa thams cad phyir zlog tu gsol /
NK041(di)021:1001: nad rims me ltar mched pa /
NK041(di)021:1003: rmis ltas mtshan ma ngan pa thams cad phyir bzlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:1004: nad rims bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi dang /
NK041(di)021:1005: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu zlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)021:1006: glo bur brgyad cu rtsa gcig gi gnod pa thams cad phyir byis pa'i gdon chen bco lnga /
NK041(di)021:1007: ya bdud rgyal po'i gnod pa /
NK041(di)021:1008: ma bdud mo 'dre mo'i gnod pa /
NK041(di)021:1009: dam log dam sri'i gnod pa dang /
NK041(di)021:1014: bzhi gshed drug 'gram bdun zur phyogs ngan bdud gcod
NK041(di)021:1015: sdang dgra gnod byed thams cad phyir zlog tu gsol
NK041(di)021:1016: / lo zla zhag dang za ma'i kag ngan phung 'dre phung sri /
NK041(di)021:1017: dbul sri mi la bse rag ltog 'dre 'gong po
NK041(di)021:1018: phyugs kyi god kha thams cad phyir zlog dpal la
NK041(di)021:1019: 'jab pa srid la rku ba dmag sna rkun sna
NK041(di)021:1020: zug pa thams cad dran pa mi gsal bar rmug
NK041(di)021:1021: cing 'thib pa mi kha dang smras gtong ba /
NK041(di)021:1023: mtshan mo'i rmi lam ngan pa thams cad tshe 'di'i rkyen dang byur /
NK041(di)021:1024: dam pa'i chos sgrub pa'i bgegs /
NK041(di)021:1025: phyi ma'i sa lam la gnod pa'i 'gal rkyen bar
NK041(di)021:1026: du gcod pa thams cad mdor na bkra mi shis
NK041(di)021:1027: pa'i rigs su gyur pa gang yin pa de dag
NK041(di)021:1028: thams cad bdag la sdang dgra gnod byed bsam ngan
NK041(di)021:1029: sbyor rtsub / do bdo phod 'dzug bsam ngan log
NK041(di)021:1030: par lta bar byed pa'i steng du da lta nyid
NK041(di)021:1033: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa la legs pa'i yon
NK041(di)021:1034: tan mtha' dag 'bad med lhun grub tu zla ba
NK041(di)021:1035: yar gyi ngo ltar 'phel zhing rgyas par mdzad du
NK041(di)021:1037: thu ba brdab sum+b+ha ni sogs drag sngags gang shes brjod /
NK041(di)021:1038: mthar zlog bya zlog byed dang bral ba'i ngang la dmigs med yun ring bzhag rol mo bya /
NK041(di)021:1039: de nas dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang sogs nas /
NK041(di)021:1040: de de bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig par brjod /
NK041(di)021:1041: ye shes kyi khro bo'i sprul pa bya khyung mthing
NK041(di)021:1042: nag rab tu 'bar bas zhal phar gzigs te 'byung
NK041(di)021:1043: po'i phyir snyogs nam yang mi thar ba'i rjes bcad
NK041(di)021:1044: par gyur / khrmo ga ru ta tsa le tsa le h'u phata /
NK041(di)021:1045: zhes gto yas kyi rjes phyi bcad /
NK041(di)021:1047: rdo rje'i sa gzhi rwa ba dra ba gur bla
NK041(di)021:1048: bre dang bcas pa sra zhing brtan pa'i phyi rol
NK041(di)021:1049: du mtshon cha sna tshogs pa'i gur khang ye shes
NK041(di)021:1050: kyi me rab tu 'bar zhing khro bo drag sngags
NK041(di)021:1051: sgrog pa rdul ltar 'tshubs pas bskal pa'i rlung yang
NK041(di)021:1052: rgyu bar mi nus par gyur /
NK041(di)021:1053: ces bsgoms la nang du log /
NK041(di)021:1054: srung ba'i 'khor lo'i nang du mdun bskyed sgrol ma
NK041(di)021:1055: 'khor bcas bzhugs pa'i skyabs sbyin phyag rgya'i 'og tu
NK041(di)021:1056: bdag cag bsrung bya 'khor bcas tshud pas gegs dang
NK041(di)021:1057: bar chad mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad las rnam
NK041(di)021:1058: par rgyal bar gyur para mosa so //
NK041(di)021:1059: gsum pa rjes kyi bya ba ni /
NK041(di)021:1060: mchod pa gsar du barje ba'am kha gsos la /
NK041(di)021:1061: byin rlabs nas bzung tshigs bcad dang sngags kyis 'bul pa gong smos ltar rgyas par bya /
NK041(di)021:1062: phyag 'tshal nyer gcig gi bstod pa tshar gcig gam gsum dang /
NK041(di)021:1064: rje btsun 'phags ma sgrol ma sogs yan lag bdun pa tshang bar byas la /
NK041(di)021:1065: 'dod don gsol ba gdab pa ni //
NK041(di)021:1066: 'grub par gyur cig rje btsun thugs rje can //
NK041(di)021:1067: 'phags ma khyod la bsnyen sgrub mchod pa dang //
NK041(di)021:1068: bstod cing gsol ba btab pa'i mthu byin gyis //
NK041(di)021:1069: deng nas bzung ste byang chub ma thob par //
NK041(di)021:1070: 'phags ma khyod dang rtag tu mi 'bral zhing /
NK041(di)021:1071: nad med tshe dbang longs spyod 'phel ba dang //
NK041(di)021:1072: byang chub sgrub la bar chad mi 'byung zhing //
NK041(di)021:1073: sa dang lam gyi yon tan rab rdzogs nas //
NK041(di)021:1074: bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK041(di)021:1075: rnam mkhyen rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK041(di)021:1079: de kun mgon pos bzod par mdzod /
NK041(di)021:1080: bdag cag so so'i skye bo'i bsam pa nyon mongs
NK041(di)021:1081: pa can du gyur pa'i dbang gis ting nge 'dzin
NK041(di)021:1082: mi gsal zhing bying rgod kyi dbang du gyur pa
NK041(di)021:1083: dang / yo byad la dbang ma thob pas mchod pa'i dngos po chung zhing ngan pa /
NK041(di)021:1085: cho ga bzhin du ma lcogs pa la sogs pa /
NK041(di)021:1086: nongs pa'i tshogs ci mchis pa thams cad 'phags pa
NK041(di)021:1087: thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa khyed rnams la
NK041(di)021:1088: bzod par gsol na bdag cag la 'phral dang yun
NK041(di)021:1089: du sgrib pa mi 'byung bar byin gyis brlab tu
NK041(di)021:1092: rje btsun sgrol ma 'dra bar shog /
NK041(di)021:1094: 'gro ba'i don du sangs rgyas shog /
NK041(di)021:1096: khyed kyis sems can sogs kyis ye shes pa gshegs /
NK041(di)021:1097: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu /
NK041(di)021:1098: 'dir rten dang khyad par sku gzugs yod pa'i dbang du byas nas /
NK041(di)021:1099: spyan drangs pa'i ye shes pa rnams rten 'di dag la brtan par bzhugs nas /
NK041(di)021:1100: sbyin pa'i bdag pos thog drangs sems can thams cad
NK041(di)021:1101: la mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa
NK041(di)021:1102: stsal du gsol / su pra tish+tha badz+r+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)021:1105: mgrin par +aah thugs kar h'u gis mtshan par gyur /
NK041(di)021:1106: ces pas sgo gsum bsrung ngo //
NK041(di)021:1108: ston mchog dam pa lha mi'i mchod 'os pa //
NK041(di)021:1109: sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)021:1110: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba //
NK041(di)021:1111: de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde zhi ba chags bral lha mi'i mchod 'os pa //
NK041(di)021:1112: cha sa la phyag 'tshal deng 'dir sems can gang
NK041(di)021:1113: dag de dag thams cad tshogs kyi dam pa lha
NK041(di)021:1115: dge 'dun phyag 'tshal der sems can gang dag de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)021:1116: 'byung po gang dag 'dir ni lhag gyur tam //
NK041(di)021:1117: sa'am 'on te bar snang 'khod kyang rung //
NK041(di)021:1118: skye dgu rnams la rtag tu byams byed cing //
NK041(di)021:1119: nyin dang mtshan mor chos la spyod par shog /
NK041(di)021:1120: bdag dang sbyin bdag 'khor dang bcas pa mi mthun
NK041(di)021:1121: pa'i phyogs thams cad las shin tu rgyal zhing bkra
NK041(di)021:1123: ces bkra shis brjod cing me tog gi char dang rol mo'i sgra bsgrag go //
NK041(di)021:1124: 'di ni nyin chog bya ba'i tshul yin la /
NK041(di)021:1125: zhag gsum mam bdun sogs bsgrubs kyang rung bas zhag
NK041(di)021:1126: grangs byed na nyin phyi ma rnams la mchod pa
NK041(di)021:1127: gsar du barje / 'bul gtor bzhi po nyin re bzhin bshams nas 'bul /
NK041(di)021:1128: mdos zlog kha gso ba tsam gyis chog /
NK041(di)021:1129: bdag bskyed nas bzung sa bcad bzhi pa glud lha
NK041(di)021:1130: 'dre la bsngo ba ma rdzogs par btang la rjes
NK041(di)021:1131: chog mchod bstod man chad bya /
NK041(di)021:1132: 'bul nyin mdos klud bsngo ba'i skabs mar me rnams spar /
NK041(di)021:1133: bden stobs kyi zlog pa la sogs gong smos ltar byas pas 'grub bo //
NK041(di)021:1134: spyir rje btsun sgrol ma'i mtshan dran pa tsam gyis 'jigs pa thams cad las skyob pa dang /
NK041(di)021:1135: bar chad thams cad zlog cing khyad par theg pa
NK041(di)021:1136: chen po pa rnams kyi lhag pa'i lha dang mgon
NK041(di)021:1137: skyob gcig pu pa yin pa dang /
NK041(di)021:1138: bod kha ba can gyi lha skal snyigs ma'i dus
NK041(di)021:1139: su byin rlabs lhag par myur ba yin pas bon
NK041(di)021:1140: lugs dang 'brel ba'i gto phran gzhan las kyang 'di
NK041(di)021:1141: nyid la 'bad rtsol nus na 'di phyi gnyis ka'i
NK041(di)021:1142: don chen po bde blag tu 'grub par 'gyur ba
NK041(di)021:1143: yin no // snyigs dus skye bo bsod nams dman //
NK041(di)021:1144: de las blo gros rgya chung bas //
NK041(di)021:1145: nor bu bor nas mching bu tshol //
NK041(di)021:1146: phug nor las kyang nyin lto 'dom //
NK041(di)021:1148: rgyun srol mang du thos pas na //
NK041(di)021:1149: mi nub btsas su 'di byas dges //
NK041(di)021:1151: 'di nyid dgos pa phan yon byin rlabs che bar mthong yang phyogs 'dir dang srol chung bas /
NK041(di)021:1152: rang gzhan phan 'dod kyi lhag pa'i bsam pas kun nas bslangs te /
NK041(di)021:1153: rgya ston yi ge rtsa ba dang rgyal tshab grags mchog gi yig cha la gzhi byas /
NK041(di)021:1154: yig cha gzhan las kyang legs pa'i cha blangs te /
NK041(di)021:1155: yon tan rgya mtsho blo gros mtha' yas pa'i sdes
NK041(di)021:1156: dpal spungs yang khrod ts+aa 'dra rin chen brag gi
NK041(di)021:1157: sgrub gnas su bris pa dge legs 'phel //
NK041(di)021:1158: thugs rje rab myur 'phags ma la //
NK041(di)021:1159: brten nas mi mthun g.yul gyi tshogs //
NK041(di)021:1160: zlog byed cho ga zab mo 'di //
NK041(di)021:1161: gzhan phan rgya mtsho 'byung ba'i blos //
NK041(di)021:1162: dpal spungs gdan sar chos sbyin 'phrul //
NK041(di)021:1163: rje dpon blo gros seng ge yis //
NK041(di)021:1164: bsgrubs pa'i dge tshogs dpal ldan gyi //
NK041(di)021:1165: bla ma mchog rnams thugs dgongs rdzogs //
NK041(di)021:1166: bstan pa dar zhing bstan 'dzin gyi //
NK041(di)021:1167: zhabs pad yun brtan 'gro ba kun //
NK041(di)021:1168: phan bdes rtag tu 'tsho ba sogs //
NK041(di)021:1169: dge legs rdzogs ldan rgyur gyur cig /
NK041(di)021:1170: ces pa'ang dam pa mchog gis bkra shis pa'i lha
NK041(di)021:1171: reg bcas bskul ngor t+aa'i si tu pad+ma dbang mchog
